\[
\text{Average Speed} = \frac{\text{Distance}}{\text{Time}}
\]

The coordinates of each student's point on the graph are given as follows:

- Evelyn: (1.25, 4.5)
- Briana: (2.5, 2.2)
- Carla: (4.25, 5.2)
- Debra: (5.6, 2.8)
- Angela: (6.8, 1.4)

