(3/5)^4 is (27/125) * (3/5) = 81/625.

(3/5)^5 is (81/625) * (3/5) = 243/3125.

(3/5)^6 is (243/3125) * (3/5) = 729/15625.

(3/5)^7 is (729/15625) * (3/5) = 2187/78125.

